{"tid":1672201,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔請你重視P牌問題","createTime":"2019-10-24T03:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T02:20:30.000Z","uid":282836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2aec236206badf1fad25d70f04693866ebf6d30f","tid":1672201,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:24:55.000Z","msg":"自8月中改為P牌限制後，請問五毛打手的問題有沒有改善? <br />\n明顯限制P牌解決不了五毛的問題。<br />\n<br />\n我的建議反而不應限制P牌，增加留言量，可以沖淡五毛的留言，然後改善上熱門的公式，這才是冶本的方法。<br />\n<br />\n以下這兩張圖給你參考。<br />\n<br />\n[1] 每日參與討論會員數量 <br />\n「深紅柱」＝P牌改制後<br />\n「紅柱」＝ DDOS攻擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHZwkdX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHZwkdX.png&h=58eba59f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[2]  每日留言數量<br />\n「深紅柱」＝P牌改制後<br />\n「紅柱」＝ DDOS攻擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkthfPy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkthfPy.png&h=b121986b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動最好的時間，正正是八月中改制時。<br />\n一個討論組有其哲學，成功與否，取決於參與量，越互動越成功，限制不是解決問題好方法。"},{"pid":"c5cbe1f0943bc8aa1fa037fcaefd70cbc1585b3f","tid":1672201,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"希望大家俾like我呢個post，好多五毛滲透咗：<br />\n<br />\n【瓦解分化妙計】建議連仔<span style=\"color: red;\">加設五毛、分化撚、mon post狗</span>等標籤識別功能，並以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同顏色</span>顯示該等被標籤嘅用戶名俾自己睇（標籤唔會公開，但連仔有紀錄追蹤）<br />\n <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669672\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669672</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b93079423f868aa88bf35b2d11bc7a9daa407533","tid":1672201,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"好認同，我其實都係關心運動才加入，P牌改咗之後，我都少咗俾意見，無咗投入感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d0ff1676c226a2dc83be2140566ec9f2ffb61b","tid":1672201,"uid":271253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:35:43.000Z","msg":"有時想幫手推都推唔郁，係有啲無奈，的確係減少咗投入感"},{"pid":"34b1b57baa43a4a9635cb5b1a4581e93bc667b95","tid":1672201,"uid":246419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c34f0d07f2a4a5abb8295eee8bf0951b918517da","tid":1672201,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"[3] 每日文宣提及次數<br />\n「藍線」有提及的留言量 （回文數）<br />\n「紅線」佔所有回文 百份比<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEW6TKs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEW6TKs.png&h=3d99bd67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[4] 每日新帖量<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3O72r5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3O72r5n.png&h=26a5d6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「限制」正正影響「投入感」最大元兇。"},{"pid":"fed2343262c36a02d0d46efce5ab5aa04aab3578","tid":1672201,"uid":293443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"好有道理，有圖有真相，十卜"},{"pid":"811643a10617cb83eb601a5e6ab9bf39ce0e51c7","tid":1672201,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"P牌訴苦區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad505231e14c87449ca5c97d0d013d7da1f1c19c","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b93079423f868aa88bf35b2d11bc7a9daa407533","tid":1672201,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"好認同，我其實都係關心運動才加入，P牌改咗之後，我都少咗俾意見，無咗投入感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"評分又冇得評，po又推唔郁，留言就等如不推文回覆，我連留comment都少左<br />\n仲要好日唔開po，一開po就比個正牌會員屈鳩我係「出名嘅五毛」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，宜家歧視p牌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個comment正皮仲多過負皮，我真係呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌我深黃黎架，邊忽似五毛呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實有人因為佢個留言而當左我係五毛，ban埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔信睇我琴日個po第三個留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係多得佢唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77661858fe1909a0137c16f886f69d485fad3a8","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"難聽講句，p牌同非會員根本無咩分別，爭在可以出推唔到嘅po同comment"},{"pid":"03b0c4a331ef4203fc371928cf0cec24c0a8a9d3","tid":1672201,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77661858fe1909a0137c16f886f69d485fad3a8","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"難聽講句，p牌同非會員根本無咩分別，爭在可以出推唔到嘅po同comment"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"已經無得投票，連投票數都唔俾睇，仲惨過非會員"},{"pid":"4f1c9efcb4cbdf4f5c00fe0b36cf8ed1a6c8ae91","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03b0c4a331ef4203fc371928cf0cec24c0a8a9d3","tid":1672201,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77661858fe1909a0137c16f886f69d485fad3a8","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"難聽講句，p牌同非會員根本無咩分別，爭在可以出推唔到嘅po同comment"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"已經無得投票，連投票數都唔俾睇，仲惨過非會員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"頭2個鐘睇唔到，之後可以睇<br />\n唔關p事，大家都係"},{"pid":"5bd2247f4bebffcdaef5bac694641622848a7d02","tid":1672201,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1c9efcb4cbdf4f5c00fe0b36cf8ed1a6c8ae91","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03b0c4a331ef4203fc371928cf0cec24c0a8a9d3","tid":1672201,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a77661858fe1909a0137c16f886f69d485fad3a8","tid":1672201,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"難聽講句，p牌同非會員根本無咩分別，爭在可以出推唔到嘅po同comment"},"ci